search_results.title: Manu Bhagavan
search_results.snippet: Manu Belur Bhagavan (born 1970) is an Indian American historian and professor of history and human rights at Hunter College and the Graduate Center

search_results.title: Manu Bhagavan - Hunter College - CUNY
search_results.snippet: Manu Bhagavan is a specialist on modern India and international affairs, focusing on the twentieth-century late-colonial and post-colonial periods.
